										<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/edward-simon/">Ed Simon</a></h6>
										Ed Simon is a staff writer for Lit Hub, the editor of <em>Belt Magazine</em>, and the author of numerous books, including most recently<em> Heaven, Hell and Paradise Lost, Elysium: A Visual History of Angelology,</em> and <em>Relic,</em> part of the Object Lessons series. In the summer of 2024 Melville House will release his <em>Devil's Contract: The History of the Faustian Bargain</em>, the first comprehensive, popular account of that subject.																				<div class="website">
